I think you missed a post, Cyberwolf, Kluster was helping Phobia drag the 
crates.

::Kluster::

Kluster turns his head at Phobia's little speach, raising an eyebrow.

"Lead the victory over the Iron Fist? I don't see how engines would help with 
that, seeing how mobile bases are banned from this RPG..." he pushes the last 
crate into the cargo hold, turning to Hysteria.

"Unfortunately, you're the techbot on this ship," he says, smiling good 
naturaly at the word 'unfortunatey', "So you'll be best suited to check the 
technology over. Make sure it doesn't have any bugs and stuff."
